      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "If the devices are reacting to your internal state, it suggests a far more sophisticated and integrated system than standard consumer devices possess. Standard logs would certainly capture any unusual command or data transmission, so an intentional, deep-level data exfiltration would be incredibly difficult to hide. This points back to the possibility of a very subtle, yet consistent, environmental trigger that you haven't identified, like electromagnetic interference consistent with periods of high stress. It might be worth investigating if any other electronics in the house are malfunctioning or emitting unusual signals at those precise times.",
